OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,FOn one occasion Hannah even found him
OL,7,Fhiding in the wardrobe in her bedroom
OL,8,Fafter letting himself into the
OL,9,Fproperty, and even when on remand in
OL,10,Fprison he phoned her a further 128
OL,11,Ftimes.
OL,13,FReflecting on her two-year ordeal,
OL,14,FHannah told ITV West Country: "I spent
OL,15,Fmost nights just sitting up till early
OL,16,Fhours in the morning, sitting in the
OL,17,Fdark thinking, I'm so scared, so
OL,18,Fscared in this house right now.
OL,26,@vD@_OU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
