PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,F"I don't know what to do, what to
OL,7,Fthink. I was just completely lost and
OL,8,Falone in a lot of ways."
OL,10,FShe went on to add: "It turned (my
OL,11,Flife) on its head. Obviously the huge
OL,12,Feffect it had on me was that
OL,13,Fpsychological kind of torture that I
OL,14,Ffelt I was living in and being a
OL,15,Fprisoner in my home and being lost and
OL,16,Falone and scared all the time."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@XO]rD@UOUrD@`pmsD@EpnxD@_O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
