OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,FFollowing the breakdown of their
OL,7,Frelationship, Hannah's ex-partner
OL,8,Fbegan to bombard her with phone calls
OL,9,Fand even turned up at her house,
OL,10,Fsitting in the garden and throwing
OL,11,Fstones at her window.
OL,13,FHe then started ordering food to the
OL,14,Fhouse for her before gifts, such as
OL,15,Fflowers and pieces of art also started
OL,16,Farriving.
OL,18,FHannah recalled: "I kind of put
OL,19,F(gifts) in the window because I'd be a
OL,20,Fbit like, I don't know what else to do
OL,21,Fwith these.
OL,26,@zD@ROU{D@Apm{D@Gpn
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
