PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,F"And that's when I thought, I think I
OL,7,Fknow where he is, ran into my bedroom,
OL,8,Fopened my wardrobe door. And then, lo
OL,9,Fand behold, he was sat there in the
OL,10,Fwardrobe.
OL,12,F"I just screamed and ran. All I knew
OL,13,Fwas I just needed to get out of the
OL,14,Froom."
OL,16,FAfter the discovery, Hannah made the
OL,17,Fdecision to involve the police and
OL,18,Fafter searching for him for a week,
OL,19,Fher stalker was arrested and told to
OL,20,Fstop contacting Hannah.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
