OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,FBut, Hannah said: "It was barely even
OL,7,Fa day really, after that the phone
OL,8,Fcalls started, the withheld numbers
OL,9,Fstarted."
OL,11,FShe described the calls as "more
OL,12,Fsinister" explaining: "It turned to
OL,13,Fsilent phone calls. Sometimes it would
OL,14,Fbe somebody whispering sorry or hello
OL,15,Fdown the phone."
OL,26,@nD@SOUqD@IO]sD@\OUtD@IO]tD@WOUwD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
