OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,FHannah described it as "exhausting" as
OL,7,Feach new call required reporting to
OL,8,Fthe police to document for her case,
OL,9,Fbut each time she was assigned a new
OL,10,Fofficer who needed to be filled in on
OL,11,Fthe background.
OL,13,FHer case came to court almost two
OL,14,Fyears after initially calling the
OL,15,Fpolice and on the morning the case was
OL,16,Fdue to start, her former-partner
OL,17,Fpleaded guilty to the charges against
OL,18,Fhim.
OL,26,@nD@cO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
