PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,F"It felt like I'd just fallen into a
OL,7,Fhole. I thought I had a bit more time
OL,8,Fto breathe.
OL,10,F"I'd been reassured that there would
OL,11,Fbe this trial, and he may only get
OL,12,Fmaybe five years, which I was not
OL,13,Fwanting to see someone in jail for
OL,14,Ffive years, but wanting that peace for
OL,15,Fmyself, just being like I can live my
OL,16,Flife without worrying, without looking
OL,17,Fover my shoulder, without being
OL,18,Fscared."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUzD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
