CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,FInstead, to prepare for his release
OL,7,FHannah was sent home where experts
OL,8,Fattended to fit a panic alarm in her
OL,9,Fhome and alarm all the windows to her
OL,10,Fproperty.
OL,12,FShe said: "I remember just sitting
OL,13,Fthere thinking, why? Why am I the one
OL,14,Fthat's being put into jail, even
OL,15,Fthough he's the one that's pled guilty.
OL,17,F"I have to be alarmed inside my own
OL,18,Fhome, just to walk around my house.
OL,26,@tD@KOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
