PN,43514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1776704798
OL,3,C'He was sat there in the wardrobe':
OL,4,CWoman tells of stalking experience
OL,6,F"I kind of sat on my bed with this
OL,7,Flanyard and this necklace thing with
OL,8,Fthe alarm on it. I just, I just burst
OL,9,Finto tears."
OL,11,FAsked how she was now, four years on
OL,12,Ffrom his sentencing, Hannah said:
OL,13,F"Good days and bad.
OL,15,F"I'd love to say that there's some
OL,16,Fkind of magical pill that would take
OL,17,Fall of that away, but I think that
OL,18,Fthat vigilance sits there still and
OL,19,Fthat kind of mistrust in people and
OL,20,Fmistrust in yourself in what you can
OL,21,Fshare and do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@LO]uD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
